---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services | Back to Wellness Chiropractic — Chiropractic Care, SoftWave & Red Light Therapy">
  <Header />
  <main id="main-content">
    <section class="page-banner">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <h1>Our Services</h1>
        <p>Personalized chiropractic care and advanced drug-free therapies designed to help you heal with confidence.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Service 1: Chiropractic Care -->
    <section class="section section-light" id="chiropractic">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <div class="twocol">
          <div data-reveal="left">
            <span class="section-eyebrow">Core Service</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">Personalized Chiropractic Care</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
              At Back to Wellness Chiropractic, we help people across Kirkwood and the greater St. Louis area find relief from back pain, neck tension, headaches, sciatica, and more — with chiropractic care tailored to your body and lifestyle.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              Our experienced team focuses on gentle, non-invasive treatment that supports real, lasting results. Every treatment plan begins with a one-on-one consultation and detailed exam to understand your unique needs and goals.
            </p>
            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;"><span style="color: var(--color-teal); font-weight: 700;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text);">Back pain and lower back care</span></div>
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;"><span style="color: var(--color-teal); font-weight: 700;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text);">Neck tension and stiffness relief</span></div>
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;"><span style="color: var(--color-teal); font-weight: 700;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text);">Headache and migraine management</span></div>
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;"><span style="color: var(--color-teal); font-weight: 700;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text);">Sciatica and nerve pain treatment</span></div>
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;"><span style="color: var(--color-teal); font-weight: 700;">✓</span><span style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text);">Injury recovery and rehabilitation</span></div>
            </div>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Request an Appointment</a>
          </div>
          <div data-reveal="right" class="twocol-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559757175-5700dde675bc?w=700&h=600&fit=crop&q=80" alt="Personalized chiropractic adjustment at Back to Wellness" width="700" height="600" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Service 2: SoftWave -->
    <section class="section section-cream" id="softwave">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <div class="twocol" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;">
          <div data-reveal="left" class="twocol-image" style="order: 2;">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576091160550-2173dba999ef?w=700&h=600&fit=crop&q=80" alt="SoftWave therapy treatment at Back to Wellness Chiropractic" width="700" height="600" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div data-reveal="right" style="order: 1;">
            <span class="section-eyebrow">Advanced Therapy</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">SoftWave Therapy</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
              SoftWave Therapy is a non-invasive treatment that uses acoustic waves to stimulate your body's natural healing process. By increasing circulation and encouraging cellular repair, it helps reduce inflammation, relieve pain, and support faster recovery without medication, injections, or surgery.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
              This therapy is especially helpful for conditions like plantar fasciitis, tennis elbow, shoulder pain, knee pain, and other joint or soft tissue injuries. It's also commonly used for chronic pain, sports injuries, and overuse conditions such as tendinitis. Many patients report noticeable relief within the first few sessions.
            </p>
            <div style="background: var(--color-teal-soft); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-teal-dark); font-weight: 500;">💡 New patients: consultation and initial SoftWave treatment for just <strong>$49</strong>.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book Your $49 Treatment</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Service 3: Red Light -->
    <section class="section section-light" id="red-light">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <div class="twocol">
          <div data-reveal="left">
            <span class="section-eyebrow">Advanced Therapy</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">Red Light Therapy</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
              Red Light Therapy uses low-level wavelengths of light to stimulate cellular activity, improve circulation, and support the body's natural healing processes. This non-invasive treatment is known for reducing inflammation, relieving joint and muscle pain, and promoting faster recovery from physical stress.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
              In addition to pain relief, Red Light Therapy is often used to support body contouring, reduce the appearance of stubborn fat, and assist with weight management goals when combined with a healthy lifestyle. It may help improve skin tone and reduce inflammation that can contribute to bloating or water retention.
            </p>
            <div style="background: var(--color-teal-soft); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
              <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-teal-dark); font-weight: 500;">💡 New patients: consultation and initial Red Light treatment for just <strong>$49</strong>.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book Your $49 Session</a>
          </div>
          <div data-reveal="right" class="twocol-image">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571019613454-1cb2f99b2d8b?w=700&h=600&fit=crop&q=80" alt="Red light therapy session at Back to Wellness Chiropractic" width="700" height="600" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Conditions Grid -->
    <section class="section section-cream" id="conditions">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <div data-reveal="up" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <span class="section-eyebrow">Conditions We Treat</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Comprehensive Care for Various Conditions</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-3">
          <div data-reveal="up"><div class="card" style="height: 100%;"><div class="card-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20"/></svg></div><h3 class="card-title">Back Pain</h3><p class="card-text">Targeted adjustments and therapies to address acute and chronic back pain at its source.</p></div></div>
          <div data-reveal="up"><div class="card" style="height: 100%;"><div class="card-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 12h8"/></svg></div><h3 class="card-title">Neck Tension</h3><p class="card-text">Gentle corrections and soft tissue work to relieve stiffness, tension, and restricted mobility.</p></div></div>
          <div data-reveal="up"><div class="card" style="height: 100%;"><div class="card-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22c5-3 9-6 9-12V5l-9-3-9 3v5c0 6 4 9 9 12z"/></svg></div><h3 class="card-title">Headaches</h3><p class="card-text">Chiropractic care that addresses cervicogenic and tension headaches by improving alignment.</p></div></div>
          <div data-reveal="up"><div class="card" style="height: 100%;"><div class="card-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12l5 5L20 7"/></svg></div><h3 class="card-title">Sciatica</h3><p class="card-text">Precise adjustments and therapies to relieve sciatic nerve pressure and radiating pain.</p></div></div>
          <div data-reveal="up"><div class="card" style="height: 100%;"><div class="card-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14 14.76V3.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0-5 0v11.26a4.5 4.5 0 1 0 5 0z"/></svg></div><h3 class="card-title">Plantar Fasciitis</h3><p class="card-text">SoftWave therapy that delivers acoustic waves to reduce plantar inflammation and pain.</p></div></div>
          <div data-reveal="up"><div class="card" style="height: 100%;"><div class="card-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"/></svg></div><h3 class="card-title">Sports Injuries</h3><p class="card-text">Recovery support for tendinitis, overuse conditions, and soft tissue injuries from athletics.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="section section-light" id="faq">
      <div class="container-wide" style="max-width: 800px;">
        <div data-reveal="up" style="margin-bottom: 3rem; text-align: center;">
          <span class="section-eyebrow">Common Questions</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Service FAQ</h2>
        </div>
        <div data-reveal="up">
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary class="faq-question">How many SoftWave sessions will I need?</summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">Many patients report noticeable relief within the first few sessions. The exact number depends on your condition, its severity, and your body's response to treatment. We'll discuss your expected treatment timeline during your consultation.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary class="faq-question">Is SoftWave Therapy painful?</summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">SoftWave Therapy is generally well-tolerated. Most patients feel mild discomfort at most during treatment. The acoustic waves create a gentle pulsing sensation, and sessions are typically short. Any post-treatment soreness usually resolves within a day or two.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary class="faq-question">Can Red Light Therapy help with weight management?</summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">Red Light Therapy may support body contouring and assist with weight management goals when combined with a healthy lifestyle. It can help reduce the appearance of stubborn fat and reduce inflammation that contributes to bloating or water retention. It's not a standalone weight loss solution but can be a helpful complement.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary class="faq-question">Do I need a referral for chiropractic care?</summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">No referral is needed. You can call us directly at (314) 394-2093 to schedule your appointment. We welcome new patients and offer same-day appointments when available.</div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="cta-band">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <div data-reveal="up">
          <h2>Find Out Which Treatment Is Right for You</h2>
          <p>Book a consultation today and let our experienced team create a personalized plan for your recovery.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Request an Appointment</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>